666
00:58:07,803 --> 00:58:10,721
姜戈和舒尔茨医生双双下山 去往...

667
00:58:15,869 --> 00:58:18,204
往前走!
Move along!

668
00:58:18,803 --> 00:58:21,721
密西西比州

669
00:58:23,543 --> 00:58:25,628
走啊 黑鬼!
Move it, boy!

670
00:58:27,172 --> 00:58:28,423
跟上了
Keep movin'.

671
00:58:28,590 --> 00:58:30,550
到那个拍卖台上去
Get on up on that auction block.

672
00:58:32,093 --> 00:58:34,470
别让泥土拖慢你们的步伐 继续前进
Don't let that mud slow you down. Keep going.

673
00:58:50,904 --> 00:58:52,155
继续前行!
Keep goin'!

674
00:58:54,616 --> 00:58:58,536
"布隆希达·沙夫特 27岁
"Broomhilda Von Shaft. Age 27,

675
00:58:58,703 --> 00:59:00,121
右脸有'r'型标志"
'r' on right cheek."

676
00:59:01,789 --> 00:59:04,042
卖给了卡尔文·坎迪
Calvin Candie.

677
00:59:04,209 --> 00:59:08,630
他拥有密西西比第四大棉花种植园: 糖果农场
He owns the fourth biggest cotton plantation in Mississippi: Candyland.

678
00:59:08,796 --> 00:59:10,131
糖果农场?
Candyland?

679
00:59:10,298 --> 00:59:11,382
哦 那你听说过了
Oh, so you've heard of it.

680
00:59:11,549 --> 00:59:13,635
没有哪个奴隶不知道糖果农场
Ain't no slave ain't heard of Candyland.

681
00:59:13,801 --> 00:59:16,471
那么 很显然 你妻子就在那...
Well, apparently, that's where your wife is...

682
00:59:16,638 --> 00:59:18,306
这就是她讨厌的主人
and that's the repellant gentleman

683
00:59:18,473 --> 00:59:22,018
希望她在房子里工作 而不是在田地里
who owns her. Let's just hope she works in the house, not in the field.

684
00:59:22,185 --> 00:59:24,312
哦 不 她不会在田地干活的
Oh, no, she ain't no field nigger.

685
00:59:24,479 --> 00:59:26,481
她... 她很漂亮
She... she pretty.

686
00:59:27,148 --> 00:59:29,067
而且也很会说话
And she talk good, too.

687
00:59:30,652 --> 00:59:32,445
但他们鞭打了她后背 然后...
But when they tore her back up and then they...

688
00:59:33,655 --> 00:59:35,823
还在她的脸上印了逃跑的"r"字母...
burned that runaway "r" on her cheek...

689
00:59:37,242 --> 00:59:38,409
他们诅咒了她
they goddamned her.

690
00:59:43,122 --> 00:59:44,499
她不是田农 但也没好到
She ain't no field nigger but she ain't good enough

691
00:59:44,666 --> 00:59:46,668
可以料理房内家务
for the house no more either.

692
00:59:46,834 --> 00:59:48,127
他们肯定会让她做情妇
They gonna try to make her a comfort girl.

693
00:59:48,294 --> 00:59:50,171
什么是情...? 噢
What's a comfort...? Oh.

694
00:59:51,089 --> 00:59:52,382
我有自由就绝对不容许
Not while I got freedom.

695
00:59:53,967 --> 00:59:55,760
我有了枪也绝不容许
Not while I got my gun.

696
00:59:58,846 --> 01:00:00,556
那我们要出价买她?
So do we offer to buy her?

697
01:00:03,184 --> 01:00:04,560
那么...
So...

698
01:00:06,145 --> 01:00:07,814
假设...
say...

699
01:00:09,983 --> 01:00:13,194
一个人想买马
a man wants to buy a horse.

700
01:00:13,361 --> 01:00:15,405
得买一匹马
Needs to buy a horse.

701
01:00:16,364 --> 01:00:19,325
他走向农场 敲场主的门
He walks up to the farmer's farm, and he knocks on the farmer's door

702
01:00:19,492 --> 01:00:21,160
问场主买马
and asks the farmer to buy his horse.

703
01:00:21,327 --> 01:00:23,121
你知道主人怎么说吗?
And do you know what the farmer says?

704
01:00:23,288 --> 01:00:25,498
他会拒绝
The farmer says no.

705
01:00:27,000 --> 01:00:31,963
那我说去他妈的场主 我要偷那匹马
Well, I say fuck that farmer, and I'm stealin' that horse.

706
01:00:32,130 --> 01:00:36,259
有道理 但那样你就成了窃马贼 会被绞死的
Fair enough. But now you're a horse thief, and they hang horse thieves.

707
01:00:36,426 --> 01:00:38,553
更别说马儿还是会回到主人身边
Not to mention the horse goes back to its original owner

708
01:00:38,720 --> 01:00:40,346
因为马仍是他的财产
because the horse is still his property.

709
01:00:40,513 --> 01:00:44,392
我们需要她 也要一张卖身契
We need her and we need a bill of sale.

710
01:00:44,559 --> 01:00:46,853
那如果我们不买她 该如何得到?
Well, if we ain't gonna try to buy her, then how we gonna get her?

711
01:00:47,937 --> 01:00:51,524
我可以提供B计划吗?
May I offer an alternative plan of action?

712
01:00:51,691 --> 01:00:53,192
说吧
Go ahead.

713
01:00:53,359 --> 01:00:57,905
那么... 他走向农场
So... the man walks up to the farmer's farm,

714
01:00:58,072 --> 01:00:59,615
敲农场主的门...
he knocks on the farmer's door...

715
01:01:00,325 --> 01:01:05,371
向场主买农场 而不是马
and asks not to buy the horse, but the farm.

716
01:01:05,538 --> 01:01:08,916
开出个惊天报价
And makes an offer so ridiculous,

717
01:01:09,083 --> 01:01:11,878
场主就不得不答应了
the farmer is forced to say yes.

718
01:01:12,754 --> 01:01:15,506
- 我们说买糖果农场?  - 不 那太贵了
- We gonna offer to buy Candyland?  - No, it's far too big.

719
01:01:15,673 --> 01:01:18,926
但显然 农场不是这位场主的全部
But apparently this farmer ain't all about the farm.

720
01:01:20,386 --> 01:01:22,430
你对曼丁哥拳击了解多少?
How much do you know about Mandingo fighting?

721
01:01:22,597 --> 01:01:23,598
什么?
What?

722
01:01:23,765 --> 01:01:26,601
你能不能巧妙伪装成
Can you convincingly masquerade as someone

723
01:01:26,768 --> 01:01:28,436
曼丁哥拳击的高手?
who is an expert on Mandingo fighting?

724
01:01:28,603 --> 01:01:29,645
为什么?
Why?

725
01:01:29,812 --> 01:01:33,441
因为我要扮演一个来自杜塞尔多夫的阔绰买家
Because my character is that of a big money buyer from Dusseldorf,

726
01:01:33,608 --> 01:01:37,028
到格林维尔想买通进入曼丁哥拳击的道路
here in Greenville to buy my way into the Mandingo fight game.

727
01:01:37,195 --> 01:01:41,115
你要扮演我聘请来的曼丁哥专家
And your character is a Mandingo expert I hired to help me do it.

728
01:01:41,282 --> 01:01:43,242
人们叫他"独眼查理"
They call that "One-Eyed Charley."

729
01:01:46,329 --> 01:01:47,789
您好
Bonjour.

730
01:01:50,875 --> 01:01:53,795
我们是来见卡尔文·坎迪先生的
We're here to see Mr. Calvin Candie.

731
01:01:53,961 --> 01:01:55,546
请进
Entraz.

732
01:01:58,049 --> 01:01:59,509
- 谢谢你  - 嗯哼
- Thank you.  - Hm-mm.

733
01:02:00,551 --> 01:02:03,179
你要我扮演奴隶贩?
You want me to play a black slaver?

734
01:02:03,346 --> 01:02:06,015
没什么比黑奴贩更低贱了
Ain't nothin' lower than a black slaver.

735
01:02:06,182 --> 01:02:09,644
黑奴贩要比黑人管家还低下...
A black slaver is lower than the head house nigger...

736
01:02:10,311 --> 01:02:12,438
哥们 那可够低贱的
and, buddy, that's pretty fuckin' low.

737
01:02:13,564 --> 01:02:15,566
那就照那样子演
Then play him that way.

738
01:02:15,733 --> 01:02:19,779
把你奴隶贩那一面展示出来
Give me your black slaver.

739
01:02:22,448 --> 01:02:27,412
219路的嘟嘟声也来了! 花生酱!
Along came the 219 Toot! Toot! Peanut butter!

740
01:02:31,165 --> 01:02:33,042
舒尔茨医生!
Dr. Schultz!

741
01:02:33,209 --> 01:02:36,421
- 再次见面太高兴了!  - 莫吉先生
- Good to see you again!  - Mr. Moguy.

742
01:02:36,587 --> 01:02:39,382
感谢你帮我营造机会
Thank you for your assistance in creating the opportunity

743
01:02:39,549 --> 01:02:42,343
- 能有这次会面  - 何足挂齿 是我该做的
- for this appointment.  - Nonsense, it's my job.

744
01:02:42,510 --> 01:02:45,346
那么这就是我久仰大名的独眼查理了
So this is the One-Eyed Charley I've heard so much about.

745
01:02:45,513 --> 01:02:47,932
是的 这位是姜戈·弗里曼
Yes, this is Django Freeman.

746
01:02:48,099 --> 01:02:50,768
姜戈 这是坎迪先生的律师 莱奥妮德·莫吉先生
Django, this is Mr. Candie's lawyer, Leonide Moguy.

747
01:02:50,935 --> 01:02:52,895
叫我莱奥就行了
Just call me Leo.

748
01:02:53,062 --> 01:02:56,232
卡尔文在凯撒大帝室 你要跟我来吗?
Calvin's in the Julius Caesar room. You all wanna follow me?

749
01:02:56,399 --> 01:02:58,693
你和坎迪先生共事多久了?
How long have you been associated with Mr. Candie?

750
01:02:58,860 --> 01:03:01,320
哦 大约11岁时 我和卡尔文的父亲
Oh, Calvin's father and I were about 11

751
01:03:01,487 --> 01:03:03,281
一起去读的寄宿学校
when we went to boarding school together.

752
01:03:03,448 --> 01:03:06,534
卡尔文的爷爷安排我进法学院
Calvin's father's father put me through law school.

753
01:03:06,701 --> 01:03:09,704
只能说我是注定要成为卡尔文家的律师
One could almost say I was raised to be Calvin's lawyer.

754
01:03:09,871 --> 01:03:11,622
也可以说你是个黑鬼
One could almost say youse a nigger.

755
01:03:12,498 --> 01:03:13,916
你说什么?
What did you say?

756
01:03:14,083 --> 01:03:16,836
- 我说...  - 没什么 他就是莽撞了点
- I said...  - Nothing, he's just being cheeky.

757
01:03:17,378 --> 01:03:21,799
见坎迪先生之前 还有我应该知道的其他事情吗?
Uh, anything else about Mr. Candie that I should know before I meet him?

758
01:03:21,966 --> 01:03:23,968
有 他有点法国崇拜
Yes, he is a bit of a Francophile.

759
01:03:24,135 --> 01:03:25,928
哪个文明人不是呢?
What civilized people aren't?

760
01:03:26,095 --> 01:03:28,347
比起坎迪先生他更喜欢法语式的先生坎迪
And he prefers Monsieur Candie to Mr. Candie.

761
01:03:29,095 --> 01:03:30,847
随他的意愿啦(法语)

762
01:03:31,142 --> 01:03:35,146
他不会说法语 别跟他说法语 会使他难堪
He doesn't speak French. Don't speak French to him, it'll embarrass him.

763
01:03:38,065 --> 01:03:40,318
快站起身来! 转过身!
Get back on top, now! Turn around!

764
01:03:40,485 --> 01:03:41,986
就这样
There you go.

765
01:03:42,153 --> 01:03:43,779
就是这样
There you go.

766
01:03:45,656 --> 01:03:47,909
你为什么想介入曼丁哥生意?
Why do you want to get in the Mandingo business?

767
01:03:50,745 --> 01:03:54,499
你不打算让你的副手做个适当的介绍吗?
You don't intend to allow your second to make the proper introductions?

768
01:03:55,249 --> 01:03:57,126
别拖延时间
Quit stalling, now.

769
01:03:57,293 --> 01:03:58,628
回答我的问题
Answer the question.

770
01:04:01,297 --> 01:04:04,717
无奈的真相? 我很无聊
The awful truth? I'm bored.

771
01:04:04,884 --> 01:04:07,261
这看起来有点意思
This seems like a good bit of fun.

772
01:04:12,183 --> 01:04:14,185
好吧 过来
Well, come on over.

773
01:04:14,352 --> 01:04:17,063
我们正有个有趣的搏斗呢
We got us a fight goin' on that's a good bit of fun.

774
01:04:21,108 --> 01:04:22,568
你陪我到吧台好吗?
Won't you accompany me to the bar?

775
01:04:31,827 --> 01:04:33,829
白人 在房间里要脱帽 连我都知道的
You don't wear a hat in the house, white man. Even I know that.

776
01:04:43,381 --> 01:04:44,799
- 舒尔茨医生  - 何其荣幸啊
- Dr. Schultz.  - What a rare pleasure.

777
01:04:44,966 --> 01:04:46,384
继续战斗 黑鬼
Keep fighting, niggers.

778
01:04:46,551 --> 01:04:49,345
- 我要补上 是荣誉  - 见到你是我的光荣
- And I might add, an honor.  - Honor to meet you.

779
01:04:49,512 --> 01:04:51,430
请坐 是我的荣幸
Please have a seat, the pleasure's all mine.

780
01:04:51,597 --> 01:04:55,101
自由人姜戈要什么就给他什么
Get free man Django here whatever he wants.

781
01:04:55,268 --> 01:04:57,562
我要甜茶和波旁酒
And I'll have sweet tea and bourbon.

782
01:05:17,206 --> 01:05:20,251
黑鬼 用你的体重优势! 就是这样
Use your weight, boy, use your weight! There you go.

783
01:05:20,418 --> 01:05:22,670
他更高更壮!
He's much bigger and stronger!

784
01:05:22,837 --> 01:05:24,422
快点!
Come on, now!

785
01:05:24,589 --> 01:05:27,091
他不按我说的做 天啊
He's not doing what I told him, for God's sakes.

786
01:05:31,178 --> 01:05:33,973
快一点 黑鬼! 这是生死之争!
Come on, now, boy! It's a fight to the death!

787
01:05:34,140 --> 01:05:37,226
你到底要不要打败他?
You either hit him or are you ain't?

788
01:05:45,234 --> 01:05:48,321
- 大块头弗雷德 加把劲!
- Big Fred, come on!

789
01:05:48,487 --> 01:05:50,031
把他转过来! 马上...
Turn him around! Now...

790
01:05:53,826 --> 01:05:58,164
黑鬼 利用你的优势! 加把劲儿啊! 发挥你的强项!
Use your strength, boy! Come on, now! Use your strength!

791
01:06:00,249 --> 01:06:02,043
就这样!
There you go!

792
01:06:03,377 --> 01:06:05,838
就是这样! 看看
There you go! Look at that.

793
01:06:06,922 --> 01:06:09,884
看吧 我告诉你要更用力
See, I told you to put some more power in there.

794
01:06:10,051 --> 01:06:12,094
按我说的做 黑鬼!
Do what I told you, boy!

795
01:06:12,261 --> 01:06:13,721
就这样!
There you go!

796
01:06:13,888 --> 01:06:16,182
- 不!  - 照我说的来!
- No!  - Do what I told ya!

797
01:06:16,349 --> 01:06:19,393
把他戳瞎 黑鬼! 戳瞎他!
Blind him black, boy! Blind him black!

798
01:06:21,812 --> 01:06:24,315
哦 不 路易吉
Oh, no, Luigi.

799
01:06:27,526 --> 01:06:31,447
哇! 哦 哈哈!
Whoo! Whoo-hoo-hoo!

800
01:06:32,073 --> 01:06:33,240
噢...
Oh...

801
01:06:43,793 --> 01:06:45,086
把他了结
Finish him.

802
01:06:49,382 --> 01:06:51,133
继续啊 了结了他!
Go on, boy, finish him!

803
01:06:55,638 --> 01:06:57,348
这就是他被叫作大块头弗雷德的原因
That's why they call him Big Fred.

804
01:06:57,515 --> 01:07:00,935
- 花的每分钱都值得  - 好吧 路易吉再见
- Worth every penny.  - Well, arrivederci, Luigi.

805
01:07:01,102 --> 01:07:03,312
现在上来吧 休息一下
Come on up, now, boy. Get yourself a rest.

806
01:07:03,479 --> 01:07:06,482
你做的很好 相当好
You did a fine job. A real fine job.

807
01:07:07,108 --> 01:07:08,818
默西迪丝
Mercedes.

808
01:07:29,922 --> 01:07:31,132
我要龙舌兰酒
Tequila.

809
01:07:41,142 --> 01:07:42,643
你叫什么名字?
What's your name?

810
01:07:44,812 --> 01:07:46,313
我叫姜戈
Django.

811
01:07:48,733 --> 01:07:50,401
你能拼写吗?
Can you spell it?

812
01:07:52,528 --> 01:07:56,574
是D-J-A-N-G-O
D-J-A-N-G-O.

813
01:07:58,075 --> 01:07:59,577
D不发音
The D is silent.

814
01:07:59,744 --> 01:08:01,328
我知道了
I know.

815
01:08:09,295 --> 01:08:12,798
莫吉先生 你来照看我的新男仆
Mr. Moguy, want you to take care of my new boy here.

816
01:08:12,965 --> 01:08:14,675
给他找个房间 带软床的
You find him a room with a soft bed,

817
01:08:14,842 --> 01:08:17,428
再找个人好好伺候下他
then you bring him up a pony to lick his pole.

818
01:08:17,595 --> 01:08:20,347
但你明早得准备到糖果农场 听清了吗?
But you be ready to travel to Candyland tomorrow morning, now, ya hear?

819
01:08:20,514 --> 01:08:21,515
听到了 先生坎迪
Yessir, Monsieur Candie.

820
01:08:21,682 --> 01:08:25,561
罗斯科 走之前给弗雷德一大瓶啤酒
Before you go, Roscoe, get Fred here a tall beer.

821
01:08:29,398 --> 01:08:32,401
好好享受 是你自己挣来的
You enjoy that, boy. You've earned it.

822
01:08:32,568 --> 01:08:33,861
是的 先生
Yessir.

823
01:08:43,370 --> 01:08:47,166
- 黑人 你叫什么?  - 他名叫姜戈·弗里曼
- What's your name, boy?  - His name is Django Freeman.

824
01:08:50,711 --> 01:08:52,338
你从哪儿把他挖来的?
Where'd you dig him up?

825
01:08:52,505 --> 01:08:55,758
一个偶然的机缘让我遇上了姜戈
A fortuitous turn of events brought Django and myself together.

826
01:08:57,468 --> 01:08:59,553
我听说过你
I've heard tell about you.

827
01:09:00,304 --> 01:09:03,057
我听说你四处散布说曼丁哥人不太强
I heard you been telling everybody them Mandingos ain't no damn good.

828
01:09:03,224 --> 01:09:05,351
大家卖的根本不值钱
Ain't nothin' nobody is sellin' is worth buyin'.

829
01:09:05,518 --> 01:09:09,730
我好奇... 什么使你成为曼丁哥专家的?
I'm curious... what makes you such a Mandingo expert?

830
01:09:11,690 --> 01:09:14,109
我好奇是什么让你如此好奇
I'm curious what makes you so curious.

831
01:09:17,404 --> 01:09:19,490
- 你说什么 黑鬼?  - 布奇 冷静
- What did you say, boy?  - Calm down, Butch.

832
01:09:20,533 --> 01:09:21,867
他无意...
No offense given...

833
01:09:22,701 --> 01:09:23,911
也没有冒犯
none taken.

834
01:09:24,078 --> 01:09:25,788
先生坎迪...
Monsieur Candie...

835
01:09:25,955 --> 01:09:29,458
如果你能直接询问我的话 就再好不过了
I'd appreciate if you could direct your line of inquiry toward me.

836
01:09:29,625 --> 01:09:31,085
第一...
One...

837
01:09:31,710 --> 01:09:34,839
你还没喝呢 能给你来点提神吗?
you do not have anything to drink. Can I get you a tasty refreshment?

838
01:09:35,005 --> 01:09:37,842
- 好的! 我要啤酒  - 极好的
- Yes! I'll have a beer.  - Wunderbar.

839
01:09:38,008 --> 01:09:39,844
罗斯科 给这位胡子先生一份啤酒
Roscoe, a beer for the man with the beard,

840
01:09:40,010 --> 01:09:41,846
我自己来个波利尼西亚珍珠潜水酒
and I will have a Polynesian Pearl Diver.

841
01:09:42,012 --> 01:09:44,098
罗姆酒尽管放
Do not spare the rum.

842
01:09:44,265 --> 01:09:47,768
医生... 我是老练的奴隶贩
Doc... I am a seasoned slaver.

843
01:09:47,935 --> 01:09:49,645
你嘛 还是个新手
You are, well, you are a neophyte.

844
01:09:49,812 --> 01:09:54,942
我只是想确定 这牛仔是否在占你便宜
I'm simply tryin' to ascertain if this cowboy here is takin' advantage of you.

845
01:09:56,402 --> 01:09:59,613
恕我直言 先生坎迪...
With all due respect, Monsieur Candie...

846
01:10:00,322 --> 01:10:02,199
我不是来寻求你的意见的
I didn't seek you out for your advice.

847
01:10:02,366 --> 01:10:04,493
我找你是要买个格斗黑人
I sought you out to purchase a fighting nigger

848
01:10:04,660 --> 01:10:07,204
市场上买不到的那种
at above top-dollar market price.

849
01:10:07,371 --> 01:10:09,915
我印象中 当你让我作观众时
Now I was under the impression, when you granted me an audience,

850
01:10:10,082 --> 01:10:12,459
就是要讨论业务了
it would be to discuss business.

851
01:10:15,170 --> 01:10:17,631
哎 我们还没讨论生意呢
Well, we weren't talkin' business yet.

852
01:10:17,798 --> 01:10:20,134
我们刚才在讨论我的好奇
We were discussin' my curiosity.

853
01:10:22,428 --> 01:10:23,429
谢谢
Thank you.

854
01:10:23,596 --> 01:10:26,307
罗斯科 可可 去外边玩
Roscoe, Coco, go outside and play.

855
01:10:28,309 --> 01:10:31,770
示巴... 你不用动
Sheba... you stay right there.

856
01:10:31,937 --> 01:10:33,480
我知道你指的不是我
I know you didn't mean me.

857
01:10:35,232 --> 01:10:37,735
- 干杯!  - 敬德国
- Prost!  - German.

858
01:10:38,652 --> 01:10:42,448
根据莫吉说的 如果我和你做生意
Now, according to Moguy, if I do business with you,

859
01:10:42,615 --> 01:10:44,658
就是和你们俩都做生意
I'm doing business with both y'all.

860
01:10:44,825 --> 01:10:47,244
他打量 你掏钱? 是这样的吗?
He does the eyeballin', you the billfold? Is that it?

861
01:10:47,411 --> 01:10:51,165
嗯 别说的那么谄媚 但差不多是的
Well, you don't make it sound too flattering, but more or less, yeah.

862
01:10:51,332 --> 01:10:52,499
嗯
Hm.

863
01:10:53,792 --> 01:10:54,793
那么...
So...

864
01:10:54,960 --> 01:10:56,879
机灵鬼...
Bright Boy...

865
01:10:57,046 --> 01:10:59,006
莫吉说你看过我的非洲货了
Moguy tells me you looked over my African flesh

866
01:10:59,173 --> 01:11:01,342
印象并不太深 是吗?
and you was none too impressed, huh?

867
01:11:01,508 --> 01:11:03,010
不是顶级好货
Not for top dollar.

868
01:11:05,179 --> 01:11:07,222
哦 既然这样 我们也没什么好谈的
Well, then, we got nothin' more to talk about.

869
01:11:07,389 --> 01:11:09,516
看看 你想从我这里买黑人强手
You see, you wanna buy a beat-ass nigger from me,

870
01:11:09,683 --> 01:11:11,936
那些就是我想卖的高手 所以...
those are the beat-ass niggers I wanna sell so...

871
01:11:12,102 --> 01:11:14,063
他不想买你出售的黑人
He don't wanna buy the niggers you wanna sell.

872
01:11:15,022 --> 01:11:18,192
他想买你不想卖的黑人
He wants the nigger you don't wanna sell.

873
01:11:18,359 --> 01:11:22,655
喔 我不出售不想卖的黑鬼
Well, I don't sell the niggers I don't wanna sell.

874
01:11:24,907 --> 01:11:28,577
这个嘛 你不想卖最好的
Well, you won't sell your best.

875
01:11:28,744 --> 01:11:31,163
也不会卖第二好的
You won't even sell your second best.

876
01:11:31,330 --> 01:11:35,000
但第三好的...? 你还是不想卖
But your third best...? You don't want to sell him either.

877
01:11:35,167 --> 01:11:39,088
但如果我出个惊天报价 你不得不考虑一下...
But if I made you an offer so ridiculous you'd be forced to consider it...

878
01:11:39,880 --> 01:11:41,924
谁知道会发生什么呢?
who knows what could happen?

879
01:11:44,259 --> 01:11:46,553
你觉得什么是惊天报价?
And what do you consider ridiculous?

880
01:11:47,554 --> 01:11:51,642
对一个有真正天赋的货色来说 那个对的人?
For a truly talented specimen, the right nigger?

881
01:11:53,394 --> 01:11:55,437
你觉得该出价多少 姜戈?
How much would you say, Django?

882
01:11:58,816 --> 01:12:00,526
一万二美金
Twelve thousand dollars.

883
01:12:05,072 --> 01:12:09,076
先生们 刚才我只对你们好奇
Well, gentlemen, you had my curiosity,

884
01:12:09,243 --> 01:12:11,161
但现在我注意到你们了
but now you have my attention.

885
01:12:24,842 --> 01:12:30,514
维利 维利 停车! 停车 啊!
Willie. Willie. Hold up! Hold up. Ah!

886
01:12:30,681 --> 01:12:33,100
- 先生们早上好  - 舒尔茨医生早上好
- Good morning, gentlemen.  - Good Dr. Schultz.

887
01:12:33,267 --> 01:12:37,187
- 今天真美啊 不是吗?  - 不能更美了
- Beautiful morning, isn't it?  - You couldn't have picked a better one.

888
01:12:37,354 --> 01:12:40,232
请跟我们一起乘维多利亚马车吧
Please, won't you take a ride with us here in the Victoria.

889
01:12:40,399 --> 01:12:41,942
噢 非常感谢
Oh, thank you very much.

890
01:12:42,109 --> 01:12:44,236
你可以把马栓到那边
You can tie your horse up back there.

891
01:12:52,453 --> 01:12:53,746
姜戈
Django.

892
01:12:58,542 --> 01:13:02,171
我与我的骨相学同事们不同的一点就是
Where I part company from many of my phrenologist colleagues

893
01:13:02,337 --> 01:13:07,509
我相信黑鬼能达到超乎聪明 超乎天赋
is I believe there is a level above bright, above talented,

894
01:13:07,676 --> 01:13:11,805
超乎忠诚的水准
above loyal that a nigger can aspire to.

895
01:13:11,972 --> 01:13:16,643
也就是 一个万里挑一的黑鬼
Say, one nigger that just pops up in 10,000.

896
01:13:16,810 --> 01:13:18,312
一个杰出的黑人
The exceptional nigger.

897
01:13:19,313 --> 01:13:21,356
天气不错啊 是不是 机灵鬼?
Bright day, huh, Bright Boy?

898
01:13:22,483 --> 01:13:23,650
太阳升起来了
Sun is up.

899
01:13:24,818 --> 01:13:26,695
照耀我们所有人
Shining on all of us.

900
01:13:31,450 --> 01:13:34,369
- 医生 请坐  - 谢谢
- Have a seat, doc.  - Thank you.

901
01:13:34,536 --> 01:13:35,829
相当荣幸
Quite an honor.

902
01:13:35,996 --> 01:13:37,706
- 荣幸的是我们  - 谢谢
- The honor is all ours.  - Thank you.

903
01:13:37,873 --> 01:13:41,251
但我坚信 一段时间后
But I do believe that, given time,

904
01:13:41,418 --> 01:13:44,379
像机灵鬼这样的杰出黑鬼...
exceptional niggers like Bright Boy here...

905
01:13:45,339 --> 01:13:47,174
会变得不是多...
become if not frequent...

906
01:13:48,425 --> 01:13:50,052
就是更多
more frequent.

907
01:13:51,804 --> 01:13:56,391
机灵鬼 你就是万里挑一
Bright Boy, you are that one in 10,000.

908
01:13:56,558 --> 01:13:59,436
咱们这规矩是跟上 不是赶上 黑鬼
The name of the game is keep up, not catch up, nigger.

909
01:14:12,324 --> 01:14:13,700
哇!
Whoa!

910
01:14:15,202 --> 01:14:18,622
- 碰抢你就死  - 大家都冷静!
- Touch your guns, you die.  - Everybody, calm down!

911
01:14:18,789 --> 01:14:20,707
我目睹了全部过程 没有伤亡
Now I saw the whole thing. No harm done.

912
01:14:20,874 --> 01:14:21,917
你在开玩笑吗?
Are you kidding me?

913
01:14:22,084 --> 01:14:24,086
- 这黑鬼刚刚...  - 我说了没有伤亡!
- This nigger just...  - I said no harm done!

914
01:14:24,253 --> 01:14:26,797
现在把手伸出来 别碰手枪!
Now take your hand off your pistol!

915
01:14:27,881 --> 01:14:30,676
布奇 你也是
Butch, that means you too.

916
01:14:31,885 --> 01:14:34,888
大家别敌对我的客人
Everybody stop antagonizing my guest.

917
01:14:36,390 --> 01:14:38,600
胡特! 起来上马
Hoot! Get back up on your horse.

918
01:14:39,351 --> 01:14:40,894
他把我锁骨弄断了!
He broke my collarbone!

919
01:14:41,061 --> 01:14:45,357
看在上帝份上 大家帮胡特上马吧
For God's sake, somebody please help Hoot here back up on his goddamn horse.

920
01:14:45,524 --> 01:14:48,569
- 是的 老板  - 哦 你还真幸运啊 黑鬼
- Yessir, boss.  - Oh, now you are one lucky nigger.

921
01:14:49,945 --> 01:14:51,321
你最好听你老板的 白人
You better listen to your boss, white boy.

922
01:14:51,488 --> 01:14:53,949
哦 我会伴随月光和你漫步
Oh, I'm gonna go walking in the moonlight with you.

923
01:14:54,116 --> 01:14:55,909
你想牵我的手?
You wanna hold my hand?

924
01:15:02,499 --> 01:15:05,169
威利 带我们回家
Willie, take us home.

925
01:15:07,421 --> 01:15:09,423
前进!
Start moving!

926
01:15:15,804 --> 01:15:17,055
把他们带出去!
Head 'em out!

927
01:16:02,684 --> 01:16:04,228
你眼睛有问题吗 小子?
You got a problem with your eyeball, boy?

928
01:16:04,394 --> 01:16:05,646
先生 没有
No, sir.

929
01:16:05,812 --> 01:16:07,314
你想让我踢你眼睛吗?
You want a boot heel in it?

930
01:16:08,523 --> 01:16:09,483
先生 不是
No, sir.

931
01:16:09,650 --> 01:16:12,694
那就别盯着我
Then you keep your goddamn eyeballs off me.

932
01:16:12,861 --> 01:16:15,989
你再那样对我翻白眼 我就给你个恨我的理由
You flash that bad look at me again, I'll give you a reason not to like me.

933
01:16:16,156 --> 01:16:17,699
黑鬼 快走!
Now move, nigger!

934
01:16:19,826 --> 01:16:21,954
你们这些黑鬼最好看清形势
You niggers are gonna understand something about me.

935
01:16:22,120 --> 01:16:23,997
我比这里的任何白人都坏
I'm worse than any of these white men here.

936
01:16:24,164 --> 01:16:27,751
不想吃苦头 就别盯着我 
You get the molasses out your ass, you keep your goddamn eyeballs off me.

937
01:16:27,918 --> 01:16:30,963
他是粗暴的那类 不是吗?
He is a rambunctious sort, ain't he?

938
01:16:31,129 --> 01:16:32,464
的确
Indeed.

939
01:16:34,967 --> 01:16:38,345
我们能停一会儿吗 我要跟我的人说几句话?
May we stop for a moment so I may put a word in my man's ear?

940
01:16:38,512 --> 01:16:42,224
你知道 我希望对糖果农场的货一见钟情
You know, I'm expecting to fall in love once I see the specimens at Candyland,

941
01:16:42,391 --> 01:16:45,477
在那之前 如果我能跟我朋友
so before that moment, it would be good if I could have

942
01:16:45,644 --> 01:16:50,023
开个机密的战略会议就更好了
a confidential strategy meeting with my confidant.

943
01:16:52,985 --> 01:16:54,820
你要告诉我你在做什么吗?
You mind telling me what the hell you doing?

944
01:16:54,987 --> 01:16:57,030
我确定布隆希达就在糖果农场
I confirmed that Broomhilda's at Candyland.

945
01:17:01,076 --> 01:17:03,662
- 你确定是她?  - 他没叫名字
- You're sure it's her?  - He didn't call her by name,

946
01:17:03,829 --> 01:17:07,207
但她是个年轻女性 背上有鞭痕 会说德语
but she's a young lady, whip marks on her back and speaks German.

947
01:17:07,374 --> 01:17:09,251
虽然这样假设不太明智
Now, while it's not wise to assume,

948
01:17:09,418 --> 01:17:11,878
但这种情况下 我想是很可靠的
in this instance, I think it's pretty safe.

949
01:17:12,045 --> 01:17:16,675
还有一点 别这么急着报复
Point being, don't get so carried away with your retribution.

950
01:17:16,842 --> 01:17:18,802
你忘了我们为何而来
You lose sight of why we're here.

951
01:17:18,969 --> 01:17:20,762
- 你觉得我忘了?  - 是的
- You think I lost sight of that?  - Yes, I do.

952
01:17:20,929 --> 01:17:23,432
别再和坎迪对着干
Stop antagonizing Candie.

953
01:17:23,598 --> 01:17:28,562
小心露馅或者更严重 我们俩都会被杀的
You're going to blow this whole charade, or more than likely get us both killed.

954
01:17:28,729 --> 01:17:33,400
而我 还不想死在美国密西西比州的奇克索郡
And I, for one, don't intend to die in Chickasaw County, Mississippi, USA.

955
01:17:33,567 --> 01:17:36,570
我没和他对着干 是想引起他的兴趣
I'm not antagonizing him. I'm intriguing him.

956
01:17:36,737 --> 01:17:39,281
你在冲这些可怜的奴隶们大喊
You're yelling abuse at these poor slaves.

957
01:17:40,282 --> 01:17:45,704
我想起那个当着孩子的面杀死他爸的男人
I recall the man who had me kill another man in front of his son

958
01:17:45,871 --> 01:17:47,664
他可是眼都不眨
and he didn't bat a eye.

959
01:17:49,082 --> 01:17:50,208
记得吗?
You remember that?

960
01:17:52,461 --> 01:17:53,795
当然记得
Yeah, of course I remember.

961
01:17:53,962 --> 01:17:57,424
你当时说 自己的命运自己掌握
What you said was that this is my world,

962
01:17:58,383 --> 01:18:00,385
而要掌握自己的命运 同流合污在所难免
and in my world you gotta get dirty.

963
01:18:01,386 --> 01:18:04,264
我现在就在同流合污
So that's what I'm doing. I'm getting dirty.

964
01:18:07,934 --> 01:18:11,104
和我的原话不完全一样 但...
Well, you're paraphrasing a tad, but...

965
01:18:12,564 --> 01:18:14,649
大意就是这样
that was the general gist.

966
01:18:18,403 --> 01:18:19,905
糖果农场见
See you at Candyland.

967
01:18:27,621 --> 01:18:30,207
好了 黑鬼们 继续走
All right, niggers, back at it.

968
01:18:31,500 --> 01:18:33,543
你也是 月光男
That means you too, Moonlight.

969
01:19:20,924 --> 01:19:23,802
哎呀 是达达尼安!
I'll be. D'Artagnan!

970
01:19:23,969 --> 01:19:27,222
小子 为什么干逃跑这种蠢事?
Now, boy, why do a fool thing like run off?

971
01:19:27,389 --> 01:19:29,474
我没办法再打了 坎迪先生
I can't fight no more, Monsieur Candie.

972
01:19:29,641 --> 01:19:30,934
你可以的
Yes, you can.

973
01:19:31,101 --> 01:19:34,646
你不一定会赢 但你小子很能打
You might not be able to win, but your ass can fight.

974
01:19:34,813 --> 01:19:37,232
斯通塞弗先生 能不能让这些臭狗闭嘴?
Mr. Stonesipher, would you please shut these goddamn dogs up?

975
01:19:37,399 --> 01:19:40,026
- 我都没办法思考了!  - 闭嘴 玛莎!
- I cannot hear myself think!  - Quiet down, Marsha!

976
01:19:40,193 --> 01:19:42,237
玛莎 别叫了! 玛莎!
Marsha, hush up! Marsha!

977
01:19:42,404 --> 01:19:43,947
别叫了! 喂!
Hush up! Hey!

978
01:19:44,114 --> 01:19:46,741
把这些臭狗从这黑鬼身边拉走!
Get these goddamn dogs away from this nigger!

979
01:19:56,251 --> 01:19:59,713
下来吧 小子... 从树上下来吧
Come on now, boy... get on out that tree.

980
01:19:59,880 --> 01:20:01,548
遵命 先生
Yes, sir.

981
01:20:24,112 --> 01:20:26,239
他不见了多久?
How long was he loose?

982
01:20:26,406 --> 01:20:29,659
昨晚 昨天
A night. Day.

983
01:20:29,826 --> 01:20:31,453
前天半夜
Half the other night.

984
01:20:32,579 --> 01:20:34,122
他逃了多远?
How far he get off the property?

985
01:20:34,289 --> 01:20:35,999
出了庄园大概20英里
About 20 miles off the prop.

986
01:20:36,166 --> 01:20:38,293
对于一个瘸子来说 算是逃得很远了
Pretty far considering that limp he got.

987
01:20:41,087 --> 01:20:44,424
莫吉先生 达达尼安这周五会和谁打?
Mr. Moguy, who was D'Artagnan supposed to fight on Friday?

988
01:20:44,591 --> 01:20:46,218
一个新人
One of this new lot.

989
01:20:47,385 --> 01:20:50,096
看他这副死人样 瞎子也不会赌他赢
Well, way he looks now, a blind Indian wouldn't bet a bead on him.

990
01:20:50,263 --> 01:20:52,766
求您了 坎迪先生 我已经没办法再打了
Please, Monsieur Candie, I ain't got it in me no more.

991
01:20:52,933 --> 01:20:54,434
- 别 别 别  - 我不行了...
- Now, now, now, now, now.  - I can't...

992
01:20:54,601 --> 01:20:57,020
别求我
Now, no begging.

993
01:20:57,187 --> 01:20:59,648
别利用我的同情心
No playing on my soft heart.

994
01:21:03,109 --> 01:21:05,654
- 你有麻烦了 小子  - 知道 先生
- You in trouble now, son.  - Yes, sir.

995
01:21:08,573 --> 01:21:12,118
我花500块买了你
I done paid $500 for you.

996
01:21:12,285 --> 01:21:17,165
这500块是要你在被别人打死之前
When I pay $500, then I expect to get five fights out of a nigger

997
01:21:17,332 --> 01:21:19,709
